      "language": "cpp",
      "code": "// Time:  O(1)\n// Space: O(1)\n\n// combinatorics\nclass Solution {\npublic:\n    int minCost(int n) {\n        const auto& nC2 = [](int n) {\n            return n * (n - 1) / 2;\n        };\n\n        return nC2(n);\n    }\n};",
